{"tid":664440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中興：內部監控失誤 並非存心欺騙美國","createTime":"2018-05-14T05:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T12:54:26.000Z","uid":5195,"like":10,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9f69c18b108c32cbb3f315698fc6074f97dbef7b","tid":664440,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"【特朗普稱會幫助中興】<br />\n【中興：內部監控失誤 並非存心欺騙】<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，正與中國國家主席習近平合作，幫助中興通訊快速恢復業務。<br />\n<br />\n中興通訊向美國商務部提出，未符合與該局和解協議，並非存心欺騙，而是因為內部監控失誤所致。<br />\n<br />\n中興要求暫緩禁止美國供應商向中興出口產品的裁決，因為禁令使公司主要經營活動無法運行，是個不成比例的懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n美國上月中宣佈，由於中興違反制裁條款，禁止美國企業七年內向中興出售零部件。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#中興通訊　#美國商務部　#制裁條款　#中美貿易　#特朗普"},{"pid":"0d57d807623d44e12e57e4f0e2128c5a02b07d61","tid":664440,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"幫你轉行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9c43daec3baedfb95fad5f4268cf813a150d05","tid":664440,"uid":14918,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:44:43.000Z","msg":"我們中國人不用求美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3baa061f4386a49b30cab02eb2886fe0bfbab46e","tid":664440,"uid":28195,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:45:05.000Z","msg":"死狗到好羞恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我nike<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9981d08073250f22e7839e768a85bbefe6fee2bc","tid":664440,"uid":33483,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"支那人係最低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843274d4454a99170470c3a6d258f329016fca48","tid":664440,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dedf302c5a513310e4cfdc96291df9e1d14971d","tid":664440,"uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":0,"